720211f-a.title: Manhattan: Greenwich Street - Park Place
720211f-a.text:
Greenwich treet, north from Park Place, showing
surface conditions under the Ninth Avenue Elevated.
The street car tracks shown are to be removed by
the Y. P. A. his location personally verified
by the writer on 9-26-1940.
June 2, 1917
W. P. A. photo
Five boroughs Project
